<section xml:id="_简介">
<title>简介</title>
<simpara>Boat是一组Java/Kotlin核心库集合（JDK 1.8+）, 主要由Kotlin编写, 广泛应用于 <link xl:href="https://github.com/srclab-projects">SrcLab</link> 里的项目.
它提供了许多方便快捷的接口, 函数和工具.</simpara>
<simpara>Boat 包括:</simpara>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-annotations/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-annotations</link>: 核心注解;</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-core/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-core</link>: 核心库;</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-serialize/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-serialize</link>: 序列化和反序列化核心库 (支持 <literal>JSON</literal>);</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-codec/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-codec</link>: 编码核心库 (支持 <literal>HEX</literal>, <literal>BASE64</literal>, <literal>SHA</literal>, <literal>MD</literal>, <literal>HMAC</literal>, <literal>AES</literal>, <literal>RSA</literal>, <literal>SM2</literal> 等);</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-id/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-id</link>: 快速ID生成框架;</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-others/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-others</link>: 第三方支持和扩展库 (如 <literal>protobuf</literal>);</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-test/">boat-test</link>: 测试库的依赖管理工程;</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-bom/">boat-bom</link>: BOM (gradle platform) project;</simpara>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
<simpara>如果你需要一次性导入常用库 (<literal>annotations</literal>, <literal>core</literal>, <literal>codec</literal>, <literal>serialize</literal> and <literal>id</literal>), 只需要导入:</simpara>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat/">boat</link>.</simpara>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</section>
<section xml:id="_获取">
<title>获取</title>
<section xml:id="_获取_boat">
<title>获取 Boat</title>
<formalpara>
<title>Gradle</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="groovy" linenumbering="unnumbered">implementation "xyz.srclab.common:boat:0.0.1"</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
<formalpara>
<title>Maven</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="xml" linenumbering="unnumbered">&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;xyz.srclab.common&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;boat&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;0.0.1&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
</section>
<section xml:id="_使用_bom">
<title>使用 BOM</title>
<formalpara>
<title>Gradle</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="groovy" linenumbering="unnumbered">api implementation("xyz.srclab.common:boat-bom:0.0.1")</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
<formalpara>
<title>Maven</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="xml" linenumbering="unnumbered">&lt;dependencyManagement&gt;
  &lt;dependencies&gt;
    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;xyz.srclab.common&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;boat&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;version&gt;0.0.1&lt;/version&gt;
      &lt;type&gt;pom&lt;/type&gt;
      &lt;scope&gt;import&lt;/scope&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;
  &lt;/dependencies&gt;
&lt;/dependencyManagement&gt;</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
<formalpara>
<title>Source Code</title>
